什么叫文艺范儿呢？The command rm (from "remove") deletes the file, and be careful! it is gone. No wastepaper basket or anything. Deleted means lost => rm (源自 "remove") 将删除某文件。请君怜惜，一眼万年。没有废纸篓或后悔药。删除就是永别。
